@SweetShop.API_HostAddress = https://localhost:7052

### ⚠️ ZALEPI TOKEN OVDE (umesto TVOJ_TOKEN_OVDE)
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..VVG8DRcYVjCRZW_yZ7RGWyXdGtAu1lSyF0v6F6wuHYc

### ============= JAVNI ENDPOINTS =============

### Login (ako trebaš novi token)
POST {{SweetShop.API_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "password": "Test123!"
}

### Lista proizvoda
GET {{SweetShop.API_HostAddress}}/api/products
Accept: application/json

### Lista kategorija
GET {{SweetShop.API_HostAddress}}/api/categories
Accept: application/json

### ============= ZAŠTIĆENI ENDPOINTS =============

### Pregled svojih adresa
GET {{SweetShop.API_HostAddress}}/api/shipping-addresses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Pregled svoje korpe
GET {{SweetShop.API_HostAddress}}/api/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Dodaj proizvod u korpu (Milka Mliječna - id=1)
POST {{SweetShop.API_HostAddress}}/api/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 2
}

### Dodaj još jedan proizvod (Lindt - id=2)
POST {{SweetShop.API_HostAddress}}/api/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 2,
  "quantity": 1
}

### Kreiraj porudžbinu (zameni shippingAddressId sa stvarnim id-jem iz baze)
POST {{SweetShop.API_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "shippingAddressId": 1
}

### Pregled svojih porudžbina
GET {{SweetShop.API_HostAddress}}/api/orders/my
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### Kreiraj Stripe PaymentIntent (zameni 1 sa stvarnim orderId)
POST {{SweetShop.API_HostAddress}}/api/payments/create-intent/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json